interactivity.to_get_this_event: Autoplays after " December 28, 2020 (Clay & Clockwork) " . This event belongs to an event chain started from " To Catch Me If I Fall " .

progression.synopsis: Now the unwilling contestant of an "Untitled Children's Show", Sensei is forced to answer a series of questions pertaining to the show's guests.
trivia: If the player has had their saved marked as a "cheater" through use of cheat codes at Sensei's laptop, they will be issued a series of punishments. They will have their affection levels with everyone reset back to zero. The only exception to this is Niki . Their affection with Ami will be raised to 1,000,000. Their save will be marked as "punished". This will prevent the player from further use of cheat codes.

changelog: This Event was added in Update .29.0.
